videos.description: Fresh off his newly signed 10-day contract with Orlando, Donta Hall deflects a pass to force a turnover and sprints to the other end to throw down a putback dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Donta Hall shows off incredible athleticism in Magic debut) 2021/4/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Donta Hall shows off incredible athleticism in Magic debut

videos.description: Nikola Vucevic pulls up for a 3-pointer as the first-half buzzer sounds vs. his former team, the Magic.
videos.headline: Vucevic beats 1st-half buzzer with 3

videos.description: Michael Carter-Williams picks off a pass and dunks it at the other end as the Magic top the Bulls.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (MCW steals and slams to seal Magic's win) 2021/4/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: MCW steals and slams to seal Magic's win
